Select or inspect the active LLM model. (Hermes parity: `hermes model`.)

Usage: model <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list  List every model the configured providers expose
  show  Print the currently-selected model
  set   Set the active model (e.g. `anthropic/claude-3.5-sonnet`)
  help  Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
